t":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, combined sunset and evening\u00a0prayers if he was undertaking a journey. And Ibn Abbas said, \u201cThe Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, combined the noon prayers and afternoon prayers\u00a0if he was on a journey, as well as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28148,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/prophet-prays-after-friday-in-his-house\/","url_meta":{"origin":41203,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Friday: The Prophet prays after Friday in his house","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would not pray after Friday prayer until he had departed and thus would pray in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 895, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 882 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4288,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/05\/fajr-rakaat-light\/","url_meta":{"origin":41203,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: The Prophet would sometimes pray lightly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would sometimes perform two cycles of prayer before the dawn prayer so lightly that I would say to myself, \"Did he recite Surat al-Fatihah?\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1165, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 724 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u00a0according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34004,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/02\/16\/muadh-salat-too-long\/","url_meta":{"origin":41203,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ease: The Prophet rebukes Mu\u2019adh for long prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal used to pray with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. Then, he returned to his people and led them in prayer. Mu'adh prayed the evening prayer and recited Surat al-Baqarah, until a man left the prayer, and Mu\u2019adh was critical of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41209,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/20\/salat-after-fajr-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":41203,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salah: No voluntary prayers after Fajr and \u2018Asr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no prayer after the morning prayer until the sun has risen, and there is no prayer after the afternoon prayer until the sun has set.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 552, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 626 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7639,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/04\/lighten-prayers-for-weak\/","url_meta":{"origin":41203,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Lighten prayer for weak, elderly, needy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud reported: A man said, \"O Messenger of Allah, I am late to prayer today because such a person makes it too long for us.\" I never saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, as angry in his preaching as he was on that day.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/41203","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.co